docs {
  # Get Instructions

  Retrieves the current system instructions (prompt) used by the agent.

  **Use case**:
  - View active behavior guidelines
  - Audit current configuration
  - Export for documentation

  **Response**:
  ```json
  {
    "instructions": "You are a TailorBlend AI Supplement Consultant...\n\n[Full system prompt here]",
    "source": "custom"  // or "default"
  }
  ```

  **Sources**:
  - `default`: Loaded from `spec/instructions.txt` at startup
  - `custom`: Runtime override via POST /api/instructions (in-memory only)

  **Note**: Custom instructions reset when API restarts.
}
